OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain in the
OL,6,Fnorthwest turning thundery. Further
OL,7,Fthunderstorms with strong gusty winds
OL,8,Fdeveloping across southwest England
OL,9,Fduring Thursday evening before
OL,10,Fspreading northeastwards overnight.
OL,11,FCan be heavy at times with the risk of
OL,12,Fsome hail. Warm and humid for all.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FRather cloudy across northern
OL,15,Fregions with outbreaks of rain and
OL,16,Fthunderstorms, accompanied by hail and
OL,17,Fgusty winds. Extreme heat transferring
OL,18,Fto eastern England, with temperatures
OL,19,Ffurther west dropping slightly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
